---
layout: layout
title: "Series - macapinlac.com"
description: "Multi-part content series and collections from Ritchie Macapinlac"
---

<div class="page-container">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-title">Series</h1>
    <p class="page-description">
      Multi-part content exploring topics in depth through connected posts and experiments.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="page-content">
    <% if all_series.empty? %>
      <div class="empty-state">
        <p>No series content available yet. Check back soon for multi-part explorations!</p>
      </div>
    <% else %>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <% all_series.each do |series_name, articles| %>
          <%= partial 'layouts/_series_card', locals: { series_name: series_name, articles: articles } %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  
  <footer class="page-footer">
    <div class="page-navigation">
      <%= link_to 'â† Back to Blog', '/', class: 'button button--secondary' %>
    </div>
  </footer>
</div> 